Ride the Ho Chi Minh Trail and experience the history of the Vietnam - American war first-hand. We cross from Vietnam into Laos and follow the original trail down south and cross back into Vietnam and end the tour in Hoi An .

This the Ho Chi Minh Trail motorcycle tour offers bikers some of the most challenging roads in Southeast Asia, as it traverses the Annamite Mountains that form a natural border between Vietnam and Laos. Our route passes through historic locations from the war, Jungle villages and at least three World Heritage sites, pristine jungle and ends in the ancient port town of Hoi An.

